{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二章讲述天争教夺命双尸宫氏兄弟在华山被神秘高手击毙后，天争教大搜华山。孙敏带着重伤的女儿凌琳和救命恩人伊风乘大车逃离华山，途中回忆伊风为救她们力战宫氏兄弟、最终同归于尽的惨烈经过。车到小镇客栈，车把式小王头和伙计宋老刀图谋不轨，被神秘出现的剑先生出手击毙。剑先生乃武林传奇人物万剑之尊，二十年来神秘莫测，他答应带孙敏等人去至友三心神君处疗伤。三心神君是武林隐世神医，武功深不可测，医术有起死回生之力，已答应为伤者医治。两位奇人以传音入密神功交谈，孙敏一行在两位绝顶高手帮助下暂获安全。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这车上的人，不是江湖大盗才怪！就连这女的，都透着些不正的味道，受伤的两个，恐怕准是被官府的公差砍伤了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真是生死关头！要不是这人——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要不是他，恐怕我也要伤在这两个煞星的掌下，现在我只是为了要看护他而多受些苦，但比起他为我们所做的，又算得了什么？",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友！好健的身手！怎地却和我兄弟动起手来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "看朋友的身手，倒很像是和死去的一个朋友一样，想来阁下也是死了一次，再活回来吧？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友！今天你就再死一次吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友！拼命也没有用。不出片刻，金衣坛里的另外三个香主也要来了。朋友！是识相的，还是认命了吧！免得等会再多吃苦。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "凌夫人！我们兄弟是先君子后小人，歹话先说在前面。夫人此刻不跟我们走，等会那三位来了，可比不上我兄弟好说话呢！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "那三位香主别的不说，可有点……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "他们三位看见夫人这般美人儿，可包不准要出什么事呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "listener": "char_gong_shen",
      "text": "姓宫的！少给天争教丢人现眼吧！用这种江湖下三门的伎俩，还在武林中道什么字号？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友！你就少管闲事吧！连自己的太太都管不了，还在这里装什么样、发什么威？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_shen",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "失陪了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管怎样，我们先往偏僻点的地方去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "首先，我该想办法将他们两人的伤治好才行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前面有歇息一会的地方吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "方才我们经过两处大镇，你都不肯打尖，现在呀，可找不到什么地方了！就是有，恐怕也是像昨天一样那种连热水都没有的小店。唉！这么赶车，真是在受活罪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "text": "随便找个地方歇下好了，等会……等会儿我再加你的车钱。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "不是我总是要你加车钱，实在因为这种天气，冒着这么大的风，晚上连口热水都喝不着，你说这个罪是不是难受？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "到了，下车吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "text": "帮我忙把病人扶下来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小王头还懂得低头呀！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "老刀子！这娘儿们来路可不正，说不定手底下也有两下子，你可得留点神！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "text": "小王头，你就心定吧！连个娘儿们都做不翻，我宋老刀还出来现什么世！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "text": "我看床上躺着的两个，八成儿是江洋大盗，说不定将他们送到官府里去，还可以领赏哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "别的我都不管，我只要这娘儿陪我睡几晚。这几天我只要一看着她，心里就痒痒的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "我小王头就是这个毛病，银子我倒不在乎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这娘儿倒睡得沉，像是玩了八次一样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "宋老刀，我得借你的床用用，不瞒你老哥说，我实在熬不住了，尤其看到这娘儿脸上的这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "你不用谢我！我也不是特地来救你的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "text": "你罪虽不致死，但也差不多了。我若不除了你，只怕又有别的妇女要坏在你的手上。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wang_tou",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "大爷饶……",
      "tone": "哀声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "你的伙伴死了，你一个人逃走，也没有什么意思吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我还有……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_dao",
      "text": "你还有什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "以后睡觉时要小心些！别的地方可没有这么凑巧，再会碰到一个像我这样的人，也住在与你同一的客栈里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "前辈……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "我是来救你的，不是来替你找麻烦的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "但是这两具尸体，却一定会替你找来麻烦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "谢谢前辈！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "受了伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "还有救吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "他武功不弱，但是伤得也很重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "你们是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "先夫凌北修……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天争教！怎地我近来总是听到这个名字？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "那么这个人叫做什么名字，你也不知道吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人倒也难得得很！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "碰到我，这也算他运气，他身受两处重伤，又经过这么些日子的奔波，受伤的确很重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_min",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "请前辈无论如何救救他们！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "你以后不要叫我前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "别人都叫我剑先生，你——你不妨也叫我这个名字吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "此地已不能久留。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "我也是四处飘游，没有一个固定的住所，不过我可以将你们带到我的一个至友之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "那里离此并不甚远，我们先到那里，治好这两人的伤再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "你会套车吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 625,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "我去将这两具尸身丢掉，你快去套车！还有，这厮虽被我点中穴道，耳朵却仍听得到，也万万留他不得！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 631,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 645,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_xin_shen_jun",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "你三根本弱，积劳又重，若再不静养，那内外交侵，便是不治之症！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 753
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_xin_shen_jun",
      "listener": "char_sun_min",
      "text": "这两人受了阴寒掌力所伤，虽然仗着根基好，但命门之火已冷，更是危在旦夕！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 755,
      "line_end": 757
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_san_xin_shen_jun",
      "listener": "char_jian_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你这厮又在嚼什么舌头！我老人家虽然多年来不问人间之事，但看在你的面上，这两人我一定管了就是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 777,
      "line_end": 779
    }
  ],
